text: Nieuw-Strijen is a polder and a former municipality in the Dutch province of Zeeland, located on the island of Tholen. The small village "Nieuw-Strijen" is now called Strijenham. Nieuw-Strijen was a separate municipality until 1813, when it was merged with Poortvliet. ==References== Category:Former municipalities of Zeeland Category:Tholen
